0:00:00.000,0:00:12.060
Ujumbe wangu utatoka katika kitabu  cha Yohana 15, mstari wa 11.

0:00:12.060,0:00:15.440
Yohana 15, mstari wa 11.

0:00:15.440,0:00:19.060
Upo hapo?

0:00:19.060,0:00:33.040
"Nimekuambia hivi ili furaha yangu iwe ndani yako na furaha yako iwe kamili."

0:00:33.040,0:00:37.220
Ina maana bila furaha ya Mungu, sisi hatuna furaha.

0:00:37.220,0:00:42.180
Kwa hivyo, jambo ambalo halijafanyika vizuri halijafanyika kabisa.

0:00:42.180,0:00:46.220
Kitu ambacho sio kamili, sio kitu.

0:00:46.220,0:00:47.700
Si sawa.

0:00:47.700,0:00:50.960
Furaha ya Mungu inafanya furaha yetu iweje?

0:00:50.960,0:00:52.720
(Kamili.)

0:00:52.720,0:00:55.460
... hufanya furaha yetu ikamilike.

0:00:55.460,0:00:57.340
Hivii ndivyo Biblia inasema hapa.

0:00:57.340,0:01:06.740
"Nimekuambia hivi ili furaha yangu iweze kuwa ndani yako na furaha yako iwe kamili."

0:01:06.740,0:01:09.400
(Amina.)

0:01:09.400,0:01:11.900
Fikiria kuhusu hilo.

0:01:11.900,0:01:17.440
Hivyo, hii inamaanisha kuwa bila furaha ya Mungu, hatuna furaha.

0:01:17.440,0:01:23.080
Kitu kisichofanyika vizuri hakijafanyika kabisa.

0:01:23.080,0:01:29.340
Usisahau Kitabu cha Yohana 16:33.

0:01:29.340,0:01:37.700
"Mambo haya nawaambieni, ndani yangu, muwe na amani."

0:01:37.700,0:01:38.520
(Amina.)

0:01:38.520,0:01:47.860
Na katika Yohana 15:11 - inatuambia kwamba bila furaha ya Mungu, hatuna furaha.

0:01:47.860,0:01:52.340
Hii inamaanisha amani ni sawa na furaha.

0:01:52.340,0:01:59.600
Amani ni sawa - yaani, neno lingine la amani ni furaha.

0:01:59.600,0:02:03.160
Ni tunda la imani - furaha!

0:02:03.160,0:02:05.540
Ni tunda la nini?

0:02:05.540,0:02:10.460
Ni tunda - kama embe kwenye mti.

0:02:10.460,0:02:15.580
Una tunda juu - mti ni imani.

0:02:15.580,0:02:24.300
Embe juu ya ... - furaha, amani, upendo.

0:02:24.300,0:02:28.500
Ni tunda la imani.

0:02:28.500,0:02:40.200
Ni tunda linalotokana na roho iliyoumbwa upya - upendo, amani, furaha.

0:02:40.200,0:02:45.360
Ina maana, bila imani, hakuna furaha.

0:02:45.360,0:02:49.280
Imani ni mti unaobeba hilo.

0:02:49.280,0:02:59.760
Hii ndiyo sababu furaha ni kitu ambacho waumini peke yao wanacho; hakuna watu wengine.

0:02:59.760,0:03:03.900
Ikiwa wewe si muuminii, huna furaha.

0:03:03.900,0:03:08.740
Furaha ni kitu ambacho waumini peke yao wanacho.

0:03:08.740,0:03:14.840
Mwambie jirani yako: "Ikiwa wewe si muumini, huna furaha."

0:03:14.840,0:03:19.020
Ikiwa wewe si muumini, huna furaha.

0:03:19.020,0:03:22.780
Sio kitu ambacho unaweza kutengeneza au kuunda mwenyewe.

0:03:22.780,0:03:25.640
Unafikiri, "Ninahitaji furaha, ninahitaji furaha."

0:03:25.640,0:03:31.320
Fedha - mamilioni ya dola hayawezi kukupa furaha hiyo.

0:03:31.320,0:03:41.820
Dunia inaweza kuwa na furaha - inapataikana katika mazingira yao na katika maeneo yao.

0:03:41.820,0:03:46.640
Dunia, kwa wale wasioamini - wanaweza kuwa na furaha.

0:03:46.640,0:03:50.460
Furaha, wanapokupa dola milioni unasema, "Oh furaha imekuja!"

0:03:50.460,0:03:55.280
Unaanza kusema, "Hey!" Lakini hii si furaha!

0:03:55.280,0:03:57.720
Siku moja unapokea simu kutoka kwa rais,

0:03:57.720,0:04:00.300
"Hey! Wanataka kukuona Ikulu!" au popote.

0:04:00.300,0:04:05.460
"Oh!" - hiyo ni raha; si furaha.

0:04:05.460,0:04:14.980
Dunia inaweza kuwa na raha - hii inapatikana  katika mazingira yao na katika maeneo yao.

0:04:14.980,0:04:18.460
huo ndio ulimwengu.

0:04:18.460,0:04:26.100
Lakini furaha ni kitu tu waumini wanacho.

0:04:26.100,0:04:27.980
Je! Wewe ni muumini?

0:04:27.980,0:04:29.120
Sikusikii.

0:04:29.120,0:04:31.340
(Ndiyo!)

0:04:31.340,0:04:32.400
Je! Wewe ni muuminii?

0:04:32.400,0:04:33.840
(Ndiyo.)

0:04:33.840,0:04:36.020
Unaelewa kile ninachosema.

0:04:36.020,0:04:40.100
Hiyo inaonyesha kwamba furaha ni nguvu yetu ya ushindi.

0:04:40.100,0:04:42.080
Hebu mtu aseme, "nguvu ya ushindi".

0:04:42.080,0:04:43.200
(Nguvu ya ushindi.)

0:04:43.200,0:04:45.940
Ikiwa huna furaha, huna nguvu - nguvu ya ushindi

0:04:45.940,0:04:49.660
Nguvu ya kushinda ugonjwa ni furaha.

0:04:49.660,0:04:52.100
Nguvu ya kushinda shida ni furaha.

0:04:52.100,0:04:54.990
Nguvu ya kuondokana na kutengwa ni furaha.

0:04:54.990,0:04:57.880
Nguvu ya kushinda taabu ni furaha.

0:04:57.880,0:05:00.480
Kama huna furaha, huwezi kushinda hili.

0:05:00.480,0:05:07.640
Biblia inasema, "Haya yote yatatokea lakini shangilia, umeshinda."

0:05:07.640,0:05:10.740
(Amina.)

0:05:10.740,0:05:14.880
Nguvu ya Ushindi.

0:05:14.880,0:05:28.380
Tahadhari; wakati wowote furaha yetu ikitoka na kutuacha tasa na tupu,

0:05:28.380,0:05:37.240
inathibitisha kwamba sisi tuko nje ya ushirika, nje ya mawasiliano na Mungu.

0:05:37.240,0:05:42.600
Wakati wowote unapoona kwamba hakuna furaha - kutoka kwa Mungu.

0:05:42.600,0:05:49.140
Huwezi kuomba - hata wakati unapoomba, hauko pale.

0:05:49.140,0:05:52.320
Ibada  ya Jumapili ya SCOAN

0:05:52.320,0:05:53.680
Sehemu ya  ziada ya kukaa ya kanisa

0:05:53.680,0:06:02.620
Wakati wowote furaha yetu ikitutoka,

0:06:02.620,0:06:10.920
inathibitisha kwamba sisi tuko nje ya ushirika, nje ya mawasiliano  na Mungu.

0:06:10.920,0:06:20.680
Wakati wowote usipopata furaha - hakuna ushirika, hakuna furaha - hakuna mawasiliano na Mungu.

0:06:20.680,0:06:25.240
Nina furaha -ndiyo sababu unaniona.

0:06:25.240,0:06:29.820
Sema, "Furaha ni nguvu yangu ya kushinda".

0:06:29.820,0:06:34.000
Ndiyo.

0:06:34.000,0:06:35.500
Nguvu ya Ushindi.

0:06:35.500,0:06:38.400
Unapokuwa na furahai, utaweza kushinda taabu.

0:06:38.400,0:06:43.020
Una shida lakini unawaambia watu, "Kwa Mungu vitu vyote vinawezekana".

0:06:43.020,0:06:46.480
Utakuwa ukicheka, unaona watu wakicheka na wenye furaha, wakati wana ...

0:06:46.480,0:06:53.560
Angalia Mtume Paulo na mwiba katika mwili wake - nenda kasome hili katika Wakorintho.

0:06:53.560,0:07:04.740
Biblia haikutuambia hasa shida aliyokuwa nayo, lakini tunajua ilikuwa ni shida kutoka shimo la kuzimu.

0:07:04.740,0:07:07.780
Ibada  ya Jumapili ya SCOAN

0:07:07.780,0:07:18.540
Kama Mkristo, majaribu yanaweza kukujaribu; hayawezi kuharibu au kuiba furaha yako.

0:07:18.540,0:07:24.900
Unapokuwa si muuminii, majaribu yatakuharibu,

0:07:24.900,0:07:28.160
yatakuangamiza kutoka katika nafasi yako,

0:07:28.160,0:07:30.440
yatakuondoa nje ya Mungu.

0:07:30.440,0:07:33.640
Ni jaribio na mateso ambayo yamesababisha haya yote leo.

0:07:33.640,0:07:38.280
Wengi wetu tunataka kurejesha uhusiano wetu na Mungu.

0:07:38.280,0:07:45.920
Unaendelea kwenda nje, nje, kwenda nje, nje, kwenda nje kwa sababu ya shida.

0:07:45.920,0:07:50.860
Unapokuwa na shida, unaanza kusema, "Kwa nini nina shida hii?".

0:07:50.860,0:07:57.260
Na hujui kwamba Shetani anatumia njia hii kukuibia furaha yako,

0:07:57.260,0:08:02.040
kukuibia uhusiano wako.

0:08:02.040,0:08:16.240
Majaribu, dhiki, umaskini, shida inaweza kukujaribu kama mtu wa imani;

0:08:16.240,0:08:20.180
lakini haziwezi kukuharibu kwa sababu ya furaha.

